{
  "stem": "18572.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- I didn't, you know?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you had said something about what did I do about clothes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Sometimes I wonder what happened that I stayed the whole time in the same clothes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But that one time that we were in hiding in the-- with the Czech man, we were in an attic, and there was a bunch of chestnuts.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And to me, this was such a wonderful thing because there was something I could sort of organize, and play with, and do things with.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Russians came into that part of Poland in February of '44.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the next thing I know is being in some sort of a house.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was-- there was some Russian soldiers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was-- one was a Russian-- I found out later he was a general.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But he was very nice-- very nice to my mother and myself.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I remember hiding under-- there was-- in the center of this room-- I don't know where this was-- there was a tablecloth that went down to the floor.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Hiding under the tablecloth.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Hiding in corners.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Not really speaking because the whole time that I was in hiding in the woods, or in the attic, or in any of the other hiding places, I could never talk because-- especially in the woods, if I spoke or made any sort of noise, not only did I they endanger us, but I would endanger all the other people that were with me.",
      "word_count": 64
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know, that time in the woods-- you know, I-- I talked about it, but my two uncles were killed during one of the raids.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And during another raid, my two cousins were killed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I don't know how my mother and I escaped, but we did.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
